00:24:03.680 --> 00:24:08.230
in a way that's much
more pronounced and so,

00:24:08.230 --> 00:24:15.310
in this case I encourage
people to read and listen.

00:24:15.310 --> 00:24:17.770
&gt;&gt; Kay Redfield Jamison: I think
