00:24:44.870 --> 00:24:51.830 position:56%
that it compels itself, I'd say even
in small fragments it does that.

00:24:51.830 --> 00:25:01.810
I think for me in all art, whether
it's a building, a sculpture,

00:25:01.810 --> 00:25:05.890
