still can be a shocking momentum

00:25:19.870 --> 00:25:21.170
to it.

00:25:21.170 --> 00:25:27.010
I think he achieves that, he
definitively achieves that kind

00:25:27.010 --> 00:25:32.310
of momentum, whatever he's
doing, when he's at his best.

00:25:32.310 --> 00:25:33.810
&gt;&gt; Kay Redfield Jamison: I
think it's sure and I think one

00:25:33.810 --> 00:25:40.470
of the things is striking in his
