00:25:47.760 --> 00:25:52.030
it's the sea over and over again,
or it's a turmoil of people over

00:25:52.030 --> 00:25:56.540
and over again, but it's
in waves, unremitting.

00:25:56.540 --> 00:25:58.530
&gt;&gt; Michael Hersch: One thing
