00:33:00.170 --> 00:33:02.630
of just incredible
gentleness and kindness

00:33:02.630 --> 00:33:06.200 position:56%
and talkingness and soft-spokenness.

00:33:06.200 --> 00:33:08.470
He's a calm, good man.

00:33:08.470 --> 00:33:14.900
So, what about the writing of
it and the words and the music,

00:33:14.900 --> 00:33:17.640
and then maybe open
it up to questions.

00:33:17.640 --> 00:33:23.350
&gt;&gt; Michael Hersch: I mean,
there's really not much to say.

00:33:23.350 --> 00:33:29.840 position:56%
The piece, you can read in the notes
